Core Packages 
Package Description
co.cask.cdap.api
Interfaces for program and resource specifications, program lifecycle, runtime context and processors.
co.cask.cdap.api.annotation
Annotations used when creating Applications.
co.cask.cdap.api.app
An Application is a logical grouping of Streams, Datasets, Flows, and other deployable elements.
co.cask.cdap.api.artifact
Classes related to artifacts.
co.cask.cdap.api.builder
Interfaces for constructing specifications.
co.cask.cdap.api.common
Commonly used utility functions.

co.cask.cdap.api.data.format
Defines data formats for use in programs and data exploration.
co.cask.cdap.api.data.schema
This package contains beta classes for schema in CDAP.
co.cask.cdap.api.data.stream
Stream specification and configuration.
co.cask.cdap.api.dataset
Defines APIs for accessing and managing data within CDAP.
co.cask.cdap.api.dataset.lib
Collection of Dataset implementations available out-of-the-box in CDAP.
co.cask.cdap.api.dataset.lib.cube

co.cask.cdap.api.dataset.lib.partitioned

co.cask.cdap.api.dataset.module
Defines deployment of custom Datasets to make them available within CDAP.
co.cask.cdap.api.dataset.table

co.cask.cdap.api.flow
Flow implementations.

co.cask.cdap.api.metrics
Defines a way to collect user-defined metrics.
co.cask.cdap.api.plugin
Packages for plugins in CDAP.
co.cask.cdap.api.schedule
For running programs periodically.
co.cask.cdap.api.service
Defines ServiceSpecification.
co.cask.cdap.api.service.http
Defines a service for handling HTTP requests.
co.cask.cdap.api.spark
Defines APIs for defining Spark jobs in CDAP.
co.cask.cdap.api.stream
Interfaces for stream interactions.
co.cask.cdap.api.webapp
For web application.
co.cask.cdap.api.worker
Configuration and specification of workers in CDAP.
co.cask.cdap.api.workflow
For constructing workflows.
co.cask.cdap.test
This package contains the public classes for unit tests.
